headline: Corteva Increases Quarterly Dividend for Fifth Consecutive Year
summary: Corteva, Inc. (NYSE: CTVA) today announced its Board of Directors has authorized a common stock dividend of $0.18 cents per share, representing an annual increase of nearly 6% over the company's previous quarterly dividend and payable September 15, 2025, to the Company's shareholders of record on September 2, 2025.
